<br>
When I had my minstrel I did +instrument testing. What I posted above was what I found. I believe +instruments and +BS work the same way as far as DD's are concerned. Remember when people said they do nothing? I have been saying all along that they change variance up to the level of the target and that they increase damage (very marginally). The first part is now standard knowledge....<br>
<br>
I don't have any +BS items. Let me find some and test ok?<br>
